rComments: He is perhaps the best prof at UofT period. Smart, insightful, very helpful and knows a lot. All around a truly gifted teacher. Too bad UofT couldn't keep him -- way to go!

Awesome prof! Very helpful, funny, and very well versed in the content. Loved the class. Easy marker
He is an exceptional teacher, very helpful and knows a great deal about the subject matter. One of the best at UofT. There should be more like him.
